&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;#8217;t forget that we want these to be optional. I would like to leave out two or three here and there.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The builder let&amp;#8217;s you do that. It looks something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

